name: Titled Sheep Game
description:
Titled Sheep Game Titled Sheep game is a clicker game that tasks you with gaining as much money as you can from your sheep farm.

Sheep Key:

White Sheep = 1 coin

Black Sheep = 5 coins

Red Sheep = 25 coins

Blue Sheep = 125 coins

Yellow Sheep = 625 coins

Building Key:

Silo = Click Increaser

Water Tower = Spawn Increaser

Windmill = Adjacency Bonus
